com.climbwithyourfeet.clustering

Class DTClusterFinder

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.climbwithyourfeet.clustering.DTClusterFinder

  • public class DTClusterFinder
extends java.lang.Object
    main class to cluster finder whose logic is based upon distance transform, density threshold, and a signal to noise argument of ~ 3 as a factor. runtime complexity ~ O(N_pixels) + ~O(N_points * lg2(N_points))
    Author:
    nichole
